WEBVTT

00:15.460 --> 00:19.960
♪During the dark night♪

00:20.100 --> 00:22.750
♪A guiding light♪

00:23.260 --> 00:25.050
♪Just like you♪

00:25.460 --> 00:29.750
♪Makes life turn bright♪

00:30.330 --> 00:35.180
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

00:35.400 --> 00:38.880
♪You gave me strength♪

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
♪Running for truth♪

00:41.800 --> 00:45.850
♪I find my path♪

00:46.600 --> 00:50.580
♪Drawing on the hope♪

00:51.200 --> 00:54.580
♪That you render me♪

00:55.130 --> 00:58.010
♪In this long journey♪

00:58.260 --> 01:01.680
♪I run on lightly♪

01:19.180 --> 01:22.980
[Reborn]
[Adapted from Qiang Yu's work, Reborn]

01:27.050 --> 01:27.750
It's chilly outside.

01:27.750 --> 01:29.020
Do you want to take a hot shower?

01:29.020 --> 01:29.980
It'll make you warmer.

01:31.750 --> 01:33.400
I didn't bring any clothes.

01:33.590 --> 01:35.430
It's fine. You can wear mine.

01:37.030 --> 01:38.400
They're all washed.

01:38.800 --> 01:39.600
They're clean.

01:40.000 --> 01:40.870
Don't worry.

01:45.870 --> 01:46.870
You're not thinking anything weird,
are you?

01:48.600 --> 01:49.920
I'm not that kind of person.

01:52.350 --> 01:53.390
Thanks.

02:13.180 --> 02:16.600
♪Under the sunlight♪

02:16.600 --> 02:20.430
♪Birds take a fly♪

02:20.430 --> 02:25.050
♪Raise me up, hold me high♪

02:25.050 --> 02:28.350
♪Only you♪

02:28.930 --> 02:33.400
♪During the dark night♪

02:33.400 --> 02:36.880
♪A guiding light♪

02:36.880 --> 02:38.500
♪Just like you♪

02:38.500 --> 02:43.450
♪Makes life turn bright♪

02:43.450 --> 02:48.570
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

02:48.570 --> 02:53.360
♪You gave me strength♪

02:53.360 --> 02:55.810
♪Running for truth♪

02:55.810 --> 03:00.850
♪I find my path♪

03:00.850 --> 03:05.080
♪Drawing on the hope♪

03:05.080 --> 03:08.680
♪That you render me♪

03:08.850 --> 03:17.680
[Episode 12]
[Where You Go, I Go]

03:34.840 --> 03:35.750
I'm off to buy something.

03:36.470 --> 03:37.150
Stay here.

03:38.120 --> 03:39.360
Don't open the curtains.

03:51.500 --> 03:55.980
♪During the dark night♪

03:55.980 --> 03:59.450
♪A guiding light♪

03:59.450 --> 04:01.080
♪Just like you♪

04:01.080 --> 04:06.030
♪Makes life turn bright♪

04:06.030 --> 04:11.140
♪Breaking free from darkness♪

04:11.140 --> 04:15.940
♪You gave me strength♪

04:15.940 --> 04:18.380
♪Running for truth♪

04:18.380 --> 04:23.430
♪I find my path♪

04:23.430 --> 04:27.650
♪Drawing on the hope♪

04:27.650 --> 04:31.250
♪That you render me♪

04:31.250 --> 04:34.600
♪In this long journey♪

04:34.600 --> 04:37.500
♪I run lightly♪

04:47.000 --> 04:47.470
What's wrong?

04:47.560 --> 04:48.909
It's been making noise.

04:48.909 --> 04:50.680
I think it's not feeling well.

04:55.750 --> 04:57.030
Go to the drawer over there.

04:57.030 --> 04:57.800
There's some medicine.

04:59.840 --> 05:01.000
The one on the left?

05:01.310 --> 05:01.910
Yes.

05:30.430 --> 05:32.120
Its leg seems injured.

05:32.360 --> 05:33.630
Did it fall?

05:35.030 --> 05:36.400
Maybe.

05:37.150 --> 05:38.560
I'll apply some ointment.
It should be fine.

05:39.430 --> 05:40.480
Be good.

05:40.480 --> 05:41.430
You'll heal soon.

05:41.830 --> 05:43.270
Don't move. Be good.

05:46.750 --> 05:47.680
It's almost done.

05:47.680 --> 05:49.310
Almost.

05:50.310 --> 05:51.360
You're amazing.

05:54.270 --> 05:55.120
It's nothing.

05:56.000 --> 05:58.270
My dad is an outstanding surgeon.

05:58.560 --> 06:00.430
No wonder he wants you
to become a doctor.

06:13.630 --> 06:14.680
Do you feel better now, Chirpy?

06:17.070 --> 06:18.430
What do you think of this name?

06:18.600 --> 06:19.120
Chirpy?

06:19.160 --> 06:19.510
Yeah.

06:19.720 --> 06:20.800
You're calling it?

06:21.160 --> 06:23.240
Because it makes this chirping sound.

06:23.510 --> 06:24.750
Doesn't it suit it well?

06:26.600 --> 06:28.000
You've come up with a name for the bird.

06:29.000 --> 06:29.720
Chirpy.

06:33.070 --> 06:33.630
Chirpy.

06:34.680 --> 06:36.120
Do you like this name, Chirpy?

06:37.390 --> 06:37.920
Chirpy?

06:38.190 --> 06:38.680
Chirpy?

06:39.270 --> 06:39.830
Do you like the name?

06:41.950 --> 06:42.630
By the way,

06:43.240 --> 06:44.630
about those two new patients,

06:44.630 --> 06:45.480
I've asked around.

06:46.040 --> 06:47.510
They're from Xianghu.

06:48.270 --> 06:49.600
So your cousin is fine.

06:49.950 --> 06:50.720
Don't worry.

06:55.270 --> 06:56.159
Thank you.

06:58.630 --> 06:59.560
No need to thank me.

07:00.160 --> 07:02.190
Anyway, I didn't think

07:02.310 --> 07:03.950
you'd be so brave

07:04.430 --> 07:05.510
to demand justice for your sister.

07:06.000 --> 07:07.270
I used to think

07:07.830 --> 07:08.870
you hated her.

07:13.430 --> 07:15.750
Qiao Beiyu and I share the same blood.

07:16.360 --> 07:18.830
It's more complex than simply liking

07:18.830 --> 07:19.830
or hating each other.

07:21.310 --> 07:23.070
I just find her pathetic.

07:23.920 --> 07:26.040
But then again, my whole family
is pathetic, right?

07:29.800 --> 07:30.360
No.

07:31.920 --> 07:33.720
If I hadn't existed,

07:34.070 --> 07:36.390
Qiao Beiyu could've grown up in Shunyun

07:36.480 --> 07:38.120
and had a completely different life.

07:38.630 --> 07:40.630
I'm the one who pushed her out.

07:41.680 --> 07:43.120
I have no right to hate her.

07:43.600 --> 07:45.070
But she has every reason to hate me.

07:50.310 --> 07:51.360
She wouldn't.

07:52.040 --> 07:53.270
You don't have to comfort me.

07:53.270 --> 07:54.750
I understand.

07:55.560 --> 07:57.920
It's because I stole her life,

07:58.240 --> 07:59.830
so I feel responsible

07:59.830 --> 08:00.920
for demanding justice for her.

08:01.120 --> 08:02.480
Even if I don't like her,

08:02.560 --> 08:03.830
I'd still do the same thing.

08:07.830 --> 08:09.480
But since Jinrui is all right now,

08:09.830 --> 08:11.040
I'm relieved.

08:13.510 --> 08:14.310
Anyway,

08:14.600 --> 08:15.680
I truly

08:15.870 --> 08:17.190
admire your courage

08:17.480 --> 08:18.270
and what you've done.

08:21.630 --> 08:23.510
Don't you think Chirpy is a lot like me?

08:24.270 --> 08:26.630
We fell right after learning to fly.

08:31.360 --> 08:32.510
Both of you will get better.

08:34.559 --> 08:35.830
But before that,

08:37.000 --> 08:38.630
let's get something to eat.

08:39.750 --> 08:41.070
Then, you'll recover faster.

08:49.160 --> 08:51.120
Thank you.

08:51.920 --> 08:52.600
Hello.

08:52.600 --> 08:53.120
See you.

08:53.120 --> 08:54.120
Is this Jiang Nian's mom?

08:55.000 --> 08:57.270
Sorry. I'm Qiao Qingyu's mom.

08:58.000 --> 08:59.920
Yes, I called a few days ago.

09:00.160 --> 09:01.600
I want to ask Jiang Nian

09:02.270 --> 09:03.950
if Qingyu has contacted her.

09:06.800 --> 09:08.000
Please think carefully.

09:08.000 --> 09:09.680
Is there anything you haven't told me?

09:10.430 --> 09:11.480
You heard about it?

09:11.920 --> 09:13.510
Yes, with all your connections,

09:13.510 --> 09:15.070
maybe you could find a way.

09:18.830 --> 09:21.680
1351339.

09:22.750 --> 09:24.720
Ma Mingkai.

09:25.920 --> 09:27.000
Try to recall it.

09:27.000 --> 09:28.510
Recall it carefully.

09:28.510 --> 09:29.160
You...

09:38.000 --> 09:38.680
Hello?

09:38.720 --> 09:39.120
Hello.

09:39.120 --> 09:40.560
Is this Qingjiang Road Police Station?

09:40.720 --> 09:42.920
Yes. Are you Qiao Qingyu's family?

09:43.070 --> 09:44.830
Yes, I'm her mother.

09:45.240 --> 09:47.510
We just pulled a female body from the river.

09:47.560 --> 09:48.390
She's about twenty.

09:51.270 --> 09:52.480
If we find her, I'll...

09:53.000 --> 09:53.630
I...

09:54.040 --> 09:55.150
I'll talk to you later.

09:56.670 --> 09:57.270
What happened?

09:57.270 --> 09:58.550
Where's my coat? I...

09:58.550 --> 09:59.630
What has happened?

10:01.510 --> 10:02.320
They pulled

10:03.600 --> 10:05.000
a female body from the river.

10:06.910 --> 10:07.790
The corpse

10:07.790 --> 10:09.200
doesn't match your daughter.

10:09.360 --> 10:10.150
The age doesn't fit.

10:10.600 --> 10:12.480
I'm afraid they've made a mistake.

10:12.480 --> 10:13.270
What are you talking about?

10:13.270 --> 10:14.840
I want to take a look.

10:15.150 --> 10:17.200
Fanghao...

10:17.550 --> 10:19.790
The ages don't match,
so there's no reason to go.

10:19.870 --> 10:20.720
Wait. Listen to me.

10:20.910 --> 10:21.630
Wait.

10:21.790 --> 10:23.320
Fanghao...

10:23.320 --> 10:25.510
I'm afraid they might make a mistake!

10:25.630 --> 10:26.790
No. It's not Qing.

10:26.790 --> 10:28.360
I'm afraid it's her.

10:28.790 --> 10:30.320
No, it's not her.

10:30.320 --> 10:31.550
If anything happens,

10:31.550 --> 10:33.390
the police will inform us, all right?

10:57.790 --> 10:58.600
Not bad, right?

11:03.870 --> 11:05.000
Are you leaving

11:07.030 --> 11:07.910
after you get better?

11:11.960 --> 11:12.600
Where will you go?

11:14.960 --> 11:18.480
Somewhere larger, with more people.

11:20.480 --> 11:23.200
Beining, Jiangzhou.

11:24.240 --> 11:25.120
Do you have money?

11:27.790 --> 11:29.510
You helped me print some materials,

11:29.510 --> 11:30.910
took me to the doctor,

11:31.320 --> 11:33.080
and let me stay at your place,

11:34.080 --> 11:35.790
I'll pay you back after this.

11:35.960 --> 11:37.360
It's just that I lost my purse.

11:37.360 --> 11:38.750
I'll pay you back as soon as I get paid.

11:38.750 --> 11:41.240
Qiao Qingyu, what do you mean?

11:42.150 --> 11:43.750
Do you think I did all this for money?

11:46.240 --> 11:47.080
Since you've decided to leave,

11:47.080 --> 11:48.080
I'll go with you.

11:48.550 --> 11:49.270
Anywhere is fine.

11:50.510 --> 11:51.320
Don't get me wrong.

11:52.790 --> 11:54.440
I've been thinking about leaving home.

11:55.630 --> 11:56.910
And it's good

11:58.240 --> 11:59.080
to have company.

12:02.200 --> 12:03.200
Besides,

12:03.200 --> 12:04.720
you get sick all the time.

12:06.150 --> 12:07.510
I'm not comfortable
with you going alone.

12:07.960 --> 12:09.480
I know you're serious,

12:10.150 --> 12:11.870
but please don't rush into anything.

12:13.440 --> 12:14.240
I'm rushing into anything.

12:14.240 --> 12:15.750
No, what I'm saying

12:16.440 --> 12:18.510
is thank you for helping me.

12:18.910 --> 12:20.720
You were so kind to come all the way
to find me.

12:21.000 --> 12:22.320
I owe you that.

12:22.320 --> 12:24.030
I helped you not because I'm kind.

12:25.870 --> 12:26.670
Well.

12:28.120 --> 12:29.080
Anyway, I'll decide

12:29.080 --> 12:30.080
for myself.

12:30.720 --> 12:31.360
You can't stop me.

12:33.080 --> 12:34.080
I just want to go with you.

12:55.510 --> 12:57.080
I insist.

13:02.080 --> 13:02.840
All right.

13:14.120 --> 13:17.290
[Missing Person: Qiao Qingyu]

13:24.150 --> 13:24.960
Mom.

13:25.910 --> 13:28.240
It's already late. We should head home.

13:31.910 --> 13:33.270
Have you seen this student before?

13:33.270 --> 13:34.320
She's from your school.

13:34.320 --> 13:34.630
No.

13:34.670 --> 13:35.960
Have you seen this girl before?

13:36.080 --> 13:36.550
No.

13:36.750 --> 13:37.440
Please take a look.

13:38.270 --> 13:39.750
Have you seen this girl?

13:39.750 --> 13:41.270
Thank you so much.

13:53.270 --> 13:53.960
Qingyu.

13:54.790 --> 13:56.550
Qingyu.

13:56.550 --> 13:57.240
Mom!

13:58.320 --> 14:00.000
What's wrong with you?
Watch where you're going!

14:00.630 --> 14:01.390
I'm sorry.

14:02.670 --> 14:03.440
Qingyu.

14:04.240 --> 14:05.000
I'm so sorry.

14:05.000 --> 14:05.790
What's it?

14:06.870 --> 14:08.630
Mom, she's not Qingyu.

14:11.720 --> 14:12.200
Anyway,

14:12.200 --> 14:13.600
we've called the police.

14:14.080 --> 14:16.000
They're more professional in searching
for missing people than us.

14:16.670 --> 14:17.960
Let's go home.

14:18.080 --> 14:18.630
Okay?

14:32.240 --> 14:33.320
There, there, Mom.

14:33.910 --> 14:34.910
Let's head back.

14:34.910 --> 14:36.480
Mom.

15:22.550 --> 15:23.120
How's my playing?

15:24.320 --> 15:25.030
Nice.

15:27.200 --> 15:28.600
I'm not playing this for free.

15:37.630 --> 15:38.750
What's this?

15:38.870 --> 15:40.670
It may not be worth much,

15:40.750 --> 15:42.150
but this is my lucky charm.

15:42.240 --> 15:44.390
I've been carrying it with me.
Here you go.

15:44.600 --> 15:46.550
Qiao Qingyu, I was just joking.

15:47.080 --> 15:47.840
I don't want it.

15:49.150 --> 15:50.080
I know.

15:50.960 --> 15:53.150
But now is the toughest,

15:53.150 --> 15:54.240
the loneliest time in my life.

15:54.750 --> 15:56.240
You're the only one by my side.

15:57.320 --> 15:58.270
This is a thank-you.

16:04.440 --> 16:07.480
All right. I'll take it.

16:10.320 --> 16:11.240
Well...

16:12.270 --> 16:13.600
This will be a token between us,

16:13.750 --> 16:15.000
but it's not a love token.

16:15.320 --> 16:16.510
I won't take advantage of you.

16:24.240 --> 16:25.120
What are you trying to do?

16:25.440 --> 16:26.720
It's nothing. Give me a moment.

16:42.840 --> 16:43.870
A gift in return.

16:50.720 --> 16:51.600
You know what?

16:52.030 --> 16:53.150
I noticed it

16:53.150 --> 16:54.320
when I first moved here.

16:54.960 --> 16:57.790
To be fair, I met it

16:58.030 --> 16:59.030
before you.

17:12.200 --> 17:14.390
I think I'll sleep

17:14.390 --> 17:15.440
in the chair tonight.

17:16.150 --> 17:17.000
No.

17:17.319 --> 17:20.000
You'll sleep here tonight. Take the bed.

17:20.390 --> 17:22.240
I'll sleep on the carpet.

17:23.670 --> 17:25.319
Oh, right.

17:59.360 --> 18:00.440
Well, the rope barely

18:00.840 --> 18:01.840
holds tight.

18:02.320 --> 18:03.320
I'm a gentleman.

18:03.320 --> 18:05.200
I won't peek at you. So don't worry.

18:13.840 --> 18:14.600
Qiao Qingyu,

18:15.270 --> 18:17.390
how about I tell you a bedtime story?

18:19.320 --> 18:20.000
Hmm.

18:20.720 --> 18:21.360
Do you remember

18:21.360 --> 18:23.120
the first time we met?

18:25.910 --> 18:27.350
You were in a fight.

18:27.960 --> 18:29.680
Also, you teased me at the riverside.

18:29.720 --> 18:30.920
You wanted me to pay for a tree.

18:32.830 --> 18:34.480
But then, I bit you.

18:34.640 --> 18:35.830
I guess we're even.

18:40.480 --> 18:42.030
Actually, that wasn't our first meeting.

18:47.590 --> 18:48.790
I remember five years ago

18:49.750 --> 18:52.310
when I went to Huanzhou Theater
to see my mom.

18:53.350 --> 18:55.680
Sheng, wait here.

18:55.680 --> 18:57.200
Your mom will meet you

18:57.200 --> 18:58.480
once she's done.

18:59.030 --> 19:00.070
Everyone, hurry up.

19:00.240 --> 19:01.480
We have a meeting in ten minutes.

19:02.720 --> 19:04.030
Three, two, three, four.

19:04.030 --> 19:05.790
Five, foot out.

19:05.790 --> 19:07.480
Five, six, seven, go.

19:07.480 --> 19:09.240
One, two, three, four,

19:09.240 --> 19:10.920
five, six, seven, eight.

19:11.030 --> 19:12.790
Two, two, three, four,

19:12.790 --> 19:14.440
five, six, seven, eight.

19:14.440 --> 19:16.160
Three, two, three, four,

19:16.160 --> 19:17.680
five, six, seven, eight.

19:17.920 --> 19:19.310
Four, two, three, four.

19:19.350 --> 19:20.400
Stop.

19:20.480 --> 19:21.680
Remember the moves

19:21.680 --> 19:22.550
I just mentioned.

19:22.550 --> 19:24.160
It's almost time. Go put on your makeup.

20:23.350 --> 20:26.830
One, two, three, four,

20:27.350 --> 20:30.480
five, six, seven, eight.

20:31.000 --> 20:34.070
Two, two, three, four,

20:34.510 --> 20:36.640
five, six, seven.

21:48.070 --> 21:49.070
I never expected

21:49.790 --> 21:51.830
to see you again after five years.

21:53.310 --> 21:54.240
But

21:55.270 --> 21:57.110
I recognized you the moment I saw you.

21:59.960 --> 22:01.000
You were peeking at me.

22:02.440 --> 22:03.550
I didn't.

22:04.310 --> 22:05.640
You started dancing.

22:05.880 --> 22:06.830
Besides, you should thank me

22:06.830 --> 22:08.270
for improvising on the piano for you.

22:08.830 --> 22:09.830
Honestly,

22:10.720 --> 22:12.000
you were cuter

22:12.030 --> 22:14.160
as a kid.

22:14.640 --> 22:16.790
People were dancing to Swan Lake,

22:17.030 --> 22:19.110
but you were dancing to Duck Pond.

22:19.310 --> 22:21.000
Don't be ridiculous.

22:24.200 --> 22:25.400
What's that noise?

22:26.790 --> 22:27.590
It's an earthquake.

22:27.880 --> 22:28.680
Earthquake?

22:28.680 --> 22:29.830
It's an earthquake. Come with me.

22:29.830 --> 22:30.510
Earthquake?

22:35.310 --> 22:36.830
Don't worry. I once read from a book.

22:36.830 --> 22:37.550
It says

22:37.550 --> 22:38.270
if you hide in the corner
of a load-bearing wall

22:38.270 --> 22:39.720
during an earthquake,

22:39.720 --> 22:40.640
you'll be safe.

22:40.830 --> 22:42.750
Plus, the tremor doesn't feel strong,

22:43.000 --> 22:44.590
so we'll be all right.

22:49.690 --> 22:54.110
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

22:54.110 --> 22:54.920
Qiao Qingyu.

22:54.920 --> 22:56.030
♪Is your name♪

22:56.030 --> 22:57.830
If it really were an earthquake,

22:58.310 --> 22:59.440
would this count

22:59.440 --> 23:00.550
as a life-and-death experience for us?

23:00.550 --> 23:01.270
Touch wood!

23:01.400 --> 23:02.790
We won't die.

23:02.790 --> 23:04.620
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

23:05.020 --> 23:08.780
♪At first sight♪

23:09.240 --> 23:10.880
Wait, if it really were?
What do you mean?

23:11.510 --> 23:13.590
Who's jumping rope

23:13.590 --> 23:14.880
at this hour of the night?

23:16.070 --> 23:17.200
You tricked me!

23:17.200 --> 23:19.330
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

23:20.000 --> 23:20.790
Qiao Qingyu.

23:20.790 --> 23:22.350
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

23:22.350 --> 23:24.830
Don't worry.
If it really were an earthquake,

23:24.830 --> 23:26.240
♪Is a place♪

23:26.240 --> 23:27.750
I'd take you with me.

23:28.090 --> 23:33.890
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

23:34.280 --> 23:37.940
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

23:38.250 --> 23:41.740
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

23:42.570 --> 23:47.430
♪Only then does time
not betray our acquaintance♪

23:49.160 --> 23:52.030
Well, what do you want me to say?

23:52.310 --> 23:54.750
You couldn't even keep an eye
on a child that age.

23:55.000 --> 23:56.400
What are you even capable of?

24:01.440 --> 24:03.200
Stop standing here.

24:03.200 --> 24:04.830
Go figure something out!

24:13.640 --> 24:15.680
Calm down.
It's useless shouting at Lusheng.

24:16.110 --> 24:17.070
They're searching for Qingyu now.

24:18.750 --> 24:20.480
Dear audience,

24:20.480 --> 24:23.110
I'm currently at Chaoyang Village.

24:23.480 --> 24:24.310
Last night,

24:24.310 --> 24:25.680
our tipline

24:25.680 --> 24:27.640
received a call for help from Madam Li.

24:27.720 --> 24:29.400
She told us her daughter,
a Grade 2 high school student,

24:29.400 --> 24:31.070
suddenly ran away from home.

24:31.070 --> 24:32.000
The exact reason

24:32.000 --> 24:33.160
remains unclear.

24:33.270 --> 24:34.000
Next,

24:34.000 --> 24:36.030
we'll head to Madam Li's place

24:36.030 --> 24:37.400
to learn more.

24:37.400 --> 24:39.590
If anyone has any information,

24:39.590 --> 24:41.680
please contact our crew immediately.

24:42.590 --> 24:44.880
The bus station, airport,
and train station

24:45.110 --> 24:46.720
have received notification
from the police.

24:47.590 --> 24:50.000
They'd let us know
as soon as there's any news.

24:52.720 --> 24:54.750
Oh. Someone from the county said

24:54.750 --> 24:56.110
they might've seen Qingyu.

24:56.750 --> 24:58.350
They're helping to identify her
from the surveillance footage now.

24:58.510 --> 25:00.640
The scanned photos will be sent over
this afternoon.

25:05.880 --> 25:07.160
Dad, please have some tea.

25:08.830 --> 25:09.640
This family

25:09.920 --> 25:11.480
is ruined by you.

25:14.350 --> 25:17.920
Why are you blaming Fanghao?

25:22.830 --> 25:24.640
Dad, Mom, the reporter is here.

25:48.720 --> 25:51.110
Honestly, I didn't want things
to turn out this way.

25:51.270 --> 25:53.160
I've tried every possible way
to communicate with them,

25:54.070 --> 25:55.790
but nothing worked on them.

25:55.790 --> 25:57.550
I couldn't get justice for Beiyu.

25:58.880 --> 26:00.680
Since the truth is out now,

26:00.680 --> 26:02.400
no matter how mad they are,

26:02.480 --> 26:03.880
they owe Beiyu that.

26:11.110 --> 26:12.680
The weather's getting colder
these days.

26:14.160 --> 26:14.750
Hmm.

26:16.070 --> 26:18.720
Remember to bundle up
when you come or leave work.

26:22.070 --> 26:23.240
I'm leaving early today.

26:23.960 --> 26:25.000
The head nurse set me up

26:25.000 --> 26:26.030
on a blind date.

26:26.400 --> 26:28.110
We'll have dinner and go for a movie.

26:28.510 --> 26:29.030
Oh.

26:30.720 --> 26:31.830
You're always busy.

26:31.880 --> 26:34.480
It's good to take a break.

26:43.110 --> 26:44.680
Have you visited Ming Sheng recently?

26:46.240 --> 26:47.830
He went to France to visit his mom,

26:48.070 --> 26:49.310
and he will be back in a few days.

26:52.880 --> 26:54.800
I saw him
outside the surgery theater yesterday.

26:55.000 --> 26:56.110
I don't think I made a mistake.

26:56.790 --> 26:58.350
He wasn't here for you?

27:42.720 --> 27:43.400
Sheng.

27:44.030 --> 27:44.720
It's my dad.

27:47.680 --> 27:48.590
Stay quiet.

28:02.110 --> 28:03.680
Wait, why are you here all of a sudden?

28:13.270 --> 28:14.790
You didn't answer my call.

28:15.720 --> 28:17.000
When did you come back?

28:17.310 --> 28:18.590
Why didn't you tell me?

28:23.350 --> 28:24.750
Why should I tell you?

28:25.200 --> 28:26.720
I got bored and came back.

28:26.720 --> 28:28.030
I'm a grown-up now.

28:28.480 --> 28:29.480
Do I have to report to you

28:29.480 --> 28:30.640
when I'm back?

28:32.550 --> 28:34.000
Why are the curtains closed?

28:34.000 --> 28:35.110
It's strange.

28:45.830 --> 28:47.160
Here's your allowance.

28:48.200 --> 28:49.550
Don't always eat instant noodles.

28:50.110 --> 28:50.920
Buy some healthy food

28:50.920 --> 28:52.160
for yourself.

28:55.030 --> 28:55.960
All right. I'm leaving.

29:03.790 --> 29:06.830
You always complain
that I treat you like a kid.

29:08.240 --> 29:09.200
Now let me ask you this.

29:09.640 --> 29:11.310
What does growing up mean to you?

29:13.880 --> 29:15.160
It means freedom.

29:16.200 --> 29:18.400
Freedom in words, thoughts,

29:18.960 --> 29:20.030
and actions.

29:23.200 --> 29:24.960
Your understanding is very limited.

29:26.240 --> 29:27.200
The freedom of growing up

29:27.200 --> 29:29.110
means you must take full responsibility

29:29.110 --> 29:31.350
for everything you do.

29:31.750 --> 29:35.070
It's a freedom
saddled with responsibility.

29:36.240 --> 29:37.790
Kids are the freest.

29:38.070 --> 29:38.880
Why?

29:38.960 --> 29:41.480
Because they have

29:41.750 --> 29:43.240
so few responsibilities.

29:48.030 --> 29:48.830
I'm off.

30:03.920 --> 30:05.830
The girl looks so nice.

30:05.830 --> 30:07.400
Why did she suddenly run away from home?

30:07.400 --> 30:08.440
I have no idea.

30:08.680 --> 30:11.240
I heard she stabbed a student at school

30:11.240 --> 30:12.960
with a knife.

30:13.030 --> 30:14.880
Seriously?

30:15.680 --> 30:17.000
The TV station

30:17.000 --> 30:18.790
and the police are looking for her,

30:18.880 --> 30:20.030
but there's no sign of her.

30:20.270 --> 30:21.240
Where do you think

30:21.240 --> 30:22.510
the Qiao family's daughter
could be hiding?

30:22.960 --> 30:23.880
No clue.

30:24.110 --> 30:26.400
I think I saw it in a series.

30:26.790 --> 30:27.400
What's it about?

30:39.830 --> 30:41.830
Am I causing you trouble?

30:42.400 --> 30:44.790
No. I'll change the lock tomorrow.

30:45.590 --> 30:47.830
My dad is like this,
showing up all of a sudden.

30:48.510 --> 30:50.440
He's a terrifying control freak.

30:50.960 --> 30:53.000
That's why I can't spend
another minute with him

30:53.110 --> 30:54.830
or go back to that cold house.

30:56.830 --> 30:59.000
Are you still hoping
for the home you had as a kid?

31:00.590 --> 31:02.110
Well, there's nothing to hope for.

31:03.030 --> 31:04.680
My mom's not coming back.

31:05.400 --> 31:07.880
That home isn't complete anymore.

31:11.350 --> 31:14.920
Aren't adults supposed to be
more reasonable?

31:15.070 --> 31:16.790
Why do they all ignore
the elephant in the room?

31:19.920 --> 31:21.000
When we were kids,

31:21.880 --> 31:23.030
they taught us

31:24.030 --> 31:26.720
to be honest, kind, and brave.

31:26.960 --> 31:28.000
But they're nothing

31:28.880 --> 31:29.960
like that.

31:31.200 --> 31:32.270
I used to think

31:32.270 --> 31:35.480
parents were honest, kind, and sincere.

31:35.920 --> 31:37.590
But then I realized

31:37.960 --> 31:40.510
they're weak, selfish, and indifferent.

31:41.110 --> 31:43.480
If everyone becomes so bad
when they grow up,

31:44.000 --> 31:45.720
I'd rather be a kid forever.

31:49.790 --> 31:50.960
Anyway, even though

31:51.440 --> 31:55.160
I'll grow fatter, taller,
and have a mustache

31:55.240 --> 31:56.270
or even wrinkles in the future,

31:56.880 --> 31:59.030
I'll always stay sincere

32:00.200 --> 32:03.400
and young at heart.

32:08.240 --> 32:09.350
I don't have a fork.

32:10.550 --> 32:11.070
Oh.

32:11.270 --> 32:12.110
Sorry.

32:12.510 --> 32:13.790
I'll get you a pair of chopsticks.

32:25.070 --> 32:28.510
You screwed me good, Jiang Xiaoli!

32:30.310 --> 32:32.000
Can you not shout here?

32:32.000 --> 32:33.160
I'll shout right here!

32:33.240 --> 32:34.550
I want everyone to hear it.

32:34.830 --> 32:35.480
I...

32:35.480 --> 32:36.350
It's Mumu.

32:36.350 --> 32:37.720
Jiang Xiaoli ruined my life!

32:37.720 --> 32:38.720
Wait here inside.

32:38.720 --> 32:39.640
I'll go out.

32:40.000 --> 32:41.030
I'll be right back.

32:43.750 --> 32:45.240
Screaming at your wife and child
in a drunken rage.

32:45.240 --> 32:46.510
You're such a loser!

32:46.830 --> 32:48.790
Punk, mind your own business!

32:49.590 --> 32:50.680
Are you out of your mind?

32:50.880 --> 32:52.440
Leave now. Stay away from this.

32:52.440 --> 32:53.110
Just go.

32:53.110 --> 32:54.000
I, Wang Zheng,

32:54.000 --> 32:55.790
had three companies

32:56.070 --> 32:57.640
with over a hundred employees.

32:57.750 --> 32:58.240
Stop shouting.

32:58.240 --> 32:58.920
Leave now.

32:58.920 --> 33:00.720
I planned immigration

33:00.720 --> 33:03.400
and my kid's university.

33:03.640 --> 33:05.400
But now I've lost everything.

33:06.200 --> 33:09.400
It's all because of you two!

33:13.000 --> 33:13.920
Are you shocked?

33:16.400 --> 33:17.590
Mumu's family has

33:18.480 --> 33:19.750
a complicated story.

33:21.310 --> 33:22.790
Her dad did well

33:22.790 --> 33:23.790
with his business,

33:24.550 --> 33:26.110
but later he got scammed.

33:26.550 --> 33:28.240
Since then, he's been down and out.

33:28.350 --> 33:30.960
He drank every day,
which hurt his liver.

33:31.680 --> 33:32.720
From then on,

33:33.720 --> 33:35.200
his temper gets worse

33:35.350 --> 33:36.590
and causes a lot of trouble at home.

33:38.030 --> 33:39.790
I feel bad for Mumu.

33:43.440 --> 33:45.270
Mumu and her mom don't have a choice.

33:46.480 --> 33:48.270
I wanted to help her.

33:49.110 --> 33:50.200
But whenever

33:50.510 --> 33:51.830
I brought it up,

33:53.000 --> 33:54.310
she would stay quiet.

33:56.000 --> 33:57.200
Everyone thinks

33:57.550 --> 33:59.920
Mumu is beautiful,

34:00.480 --> 34:01.680
smart,

34:01.680 --> 34:03.200
a class committee member,
and a top student.

34:03.350 --> 34:04.510
She's perfect.

34:06.480 --> 34:07.270
How could she hide

34:07.880 --> 34:10.110
so many secrets?

34:12.000 --> 34:13.719
Perhaps it's because she's too perfect,

34:14.199 --> 34:16.750
so she doesn't want others

34:16.750 --> 34:18.000
to see her in such a bad situation.

34:21.719 --> 34:23.159
But my dad said

34:24.270 --> 34:25.270
that her dad might not

34:25.270 --> 34:27.199
make it for more than three
to five years.

34:28.920 --> 34:29.830
Three to five years?

34:30.000 --> 34:30.480
Yes.

34:39.590 --> 34:40.199
What are you doing?

34:45.000 --> 34:46.440
Now that I've left home,

34:46.830 --> 34:49.000
do you think my parents would also...

34:49.000 --> 34:51.000
Don't over-think.

34:52.110 --> 34:53.550
You don't know
what happened in her family.

34:54.310 --> 34:55.310
Mumu doesn't like her family.

34:55.310 --> 34:56.199
Me too.

35:00.270 --> 35:00.880
I mean, my dad.

35:02.270 --> 35:02.750
Hmm.

35:40.510 --> 35:43.150
57, 58, 59, 60.

35:54.760 --> 35:57.960
36.7 degree.

36:02.110 --> 36:03.150
Actually, a fever

36:03.320 --> 36:04.550
is like your immune system

36:04.550 --> 36:05.670
leveling up to fight the invaders.

36:06.000 --> 36:07.360
If kids have a fever,

36:07.590 --> 36:09.000
it's a process of self-improvement

36:09.000 --> 36:10.510
for their immune system.

36:10.960 --> 36:12.510
It might look bad,

36:12.840 --> 36:13.960
but it's not.

36:15.000 --> 36:16.880
Congratulations,
you've cleared the level.

36:18.550 --> 36:20.840
If only growing pains

36:20.840 --> 36:22.480
were like a fever,

36:22.710 --> 36:24.880
you could swiftly clear the levels

36:24.880 --> 36:26.150
to get back on the right track in life.

36:28.320 --> 36:29.440
You've done well enough.

36:33.630 --> 36:35.440
Do you have sugar and chili here?

36:36.190 --> 36:36.760
What?

36:40.760 --> 36:42.000
Why are you pouring that in?

36:42.000 --> 36:43.190
Is that how you eat it?

36:45.670 --> 36:46.840
Does it taste good?

36:47.360 --> 36:48.670
I've been eating this way
since I was a kid.

36:50.190 --> 36:51.000
Try it.

36:53.630 --> 36:54.670
No.

36:57.480 --> 36:58.110
Oh, right.

36:58.360 --> 37:00.400
The owner of the breakfast shop
asked me

37:00.400 --> 37:02.590
why I ate a lot every day.

37:02.590 --> 37:03.760
I told him

37:03.880 --> 37:06.360
I was young and growing,
with a big appetite.

37:08.550 --> 37:11.710
Ming Sheng, I think I should go.

37:12.320 --> 37:14.480
I'm pretty much recovered.

37:14.550 --> 37:16.800
People around here started
to recognize me.

37:17.400 --> 37:19.510
Besides, you're buying
so much food every day.

37:19.630 --> 37:21.190
It'll raise suspicions sooner or later.

37:22.000 --> 37:22.630
All right.

37:24.400 --> 37:25.510
Since you've decided to leave,

37:26.670 --> 37:27.710
let's get prepared.

37:28.190 --> 37:29.150
Later,

37:29.150 --> 37:30.000
we'll make a list

37:30.000 --> 37:32.000
of everything we need for the journey.

37:35.880 --> 37:37.760
But starting tomorrow,

37:37.840 --> 37:39.480
you'll do as I say.

37:39.710 --> 37:40.670
Why should I?

37:41.510 --> 37:44.030
Because I'm more experienced
living alone than you.

37:44.440 --> 37:45.480
Because

37:45.920 --> 37:48.030
on the long life journey ahead,

37:48.960 --> 37:50.000
I'll be your only partner.

37:56.110 --> 37:56.920
Eat.

37:57.320 --> 37:58.590
We'll set off after this.

37:59.400 --> 38:00.190
Try one.

38:00.880 --> 38:01.480
Huh?

38:01.480 --> 38:02.190
Try it.

38:11.320 --> 38:11.760
Hmm.

38:12.510 --> 38:13.320
Not bad.

38:31.000 --> 38:32.590
Leave me alone. I want to drink!

38:32.590 --> 38:34.920
If I die, it's better for all of us!

38:34.920 --> 38:36.590
Get out! Two of you, get out!

38:41.280 --> 38:42.000
Sheng.

38:43.360 --> 38:44.070
Sheng.

38:54.070 --> 38:54.880
Sheng.

38:55.840 --> 38:56.630
Sheng.

38:58.590 --> 38:58.880
Sheng...

39:03.840 --> 39:06.030
Something came up at home
and I had nowhere to go,

39:06.320 --> 39:08.190
so Ming Sheng let me stay here.

39:09.550 --> 39:13.030
I see. I just wanted
to sit here for a bit.

39:13.070 --> 39:14.070
It is tough luck

39:14.070 --> 39:15.320
to have you and your daughter!

39:22.030 --> 39:23.230
Don't worry.

39:23.230 --> 39:24.960
I'll keep your secret.

39:25.550 --> 39:28.440
Since I left Nanqiao Village last time,

39:28.440 --> 39:30.070
I've been worried about you.

39:31.320 --> 39:32.320
Then yesterday,

39:33.630 --> 39:35.150
I saw on the telly

39:35.630 --> 39:36.670
that your mom was looking for you.

39:38.670 --> 39:39.760
I didn't realize

39:39.760 --> 39:41.280
things would turn out this way.

39:41.960 --> 39:43.550
Perhaps I did,

39:43.840 --> 39:45.190
but when it really happened,

39:45.440 --> 39:47.030
I didn't know how to face it.

39:50.510 --> 39:51.840
Even though I'm older,

39:52.670 --> 39:55.840
I truly admire your courage.

39:56.630 --> 39:57.760
Do you regret it?

40:02.230 --> 40:03.030
No.

40:03.550 --> 40:05.190
If I had to choose again,

40:05.710 --> 40:07.480
I'd do the same thing.

40:08.440 --> 40:11.630
Mumu, let's both
pull ourselves together.

40:14.880 --> 40:15.710
I can't.

40:17.190 --> 40:18.360
I'm not as brave as you.

40:21.670 --> 40:24.230
Well, what's your next plan?

40:26.070 --> 40:27.320
I'll leave Huanzhou.

40:30.070 --> 40:30.880
Where are you going?

40:31.510 --> 40:35.030
First to Jiangzhou.
I'll make plans later.

40:37.670 --> 40:38.710
Are you leaving alone?

40:39.400 --> 40:40.840
Sheng is going with you, right?

40:50.960 --> 40:53.190
Sheng and I grew up together.

40:54.400 --> 40:56.110
When his grandpa was still alive,

40:56.360 --> 40:58.630
he treated me like his granddaughter.

40:58.630 --> 41:00.670
He even gave me a house key.

41:01.550 --> 41:03.400
After he passed,

41:03.800 --> 41:05.960
Sheng didn't forget his promise

41:07.030 --> 41:09.920
and told me to see this place
as my second home.

41:12.190 --> 41:13.590
I know him well.

41:13.920 --> 41:16.550
He'll take the risk

41:16.550 --> 41:18.000
to hide you here.

41:19.440 --> 41:22.480
He may look wild at school.

41:22.630 --> 41:25.400
But, in fact, when we were kids,

41:25.400 --> 41:27.710
he was the one
who fed all the stray cats and dogs.

41:28.360 --> 41:29.840
Also, boys always

41:29.840 --> 41:31.960
want to be a hero.

41:32.320 --> 41:34.880
They like to show off in front of girls.

41:35.480 --> 41:36.400
Perhaps he just likes

41:36.670 --> 41:40.440
helping the needy.

41:47.960 --> 41:51.190
Honestly, I've been worried.

41:51.960 --> 41:52.880
I'm worried

41:53.550 --> 41:56.230
about him doing something
that could hurt you.

41:58.190 --> 42:00.280
No. He respects me.

42:03.030 --> 42:05.000
I didn't mean that.

42:05.320 --> 42:07.480
Sheng gets impulsive easily.

42:07.510 --> 42:09.400
I'm worried he'll do
the same thing again this time.

42:14.000 --> 42:16.670
Actually, he used to be a good kid.

42:16.960 --> 42:19.280
But after Grandpa passed away,

42:19.400 --> 42:21.280
he fell out with his dad.

42:21.480 --> 42:23.230
Plus, due to the pressure
from his studies

42:23.840 --> 42:25.510
and his plan to study abroad,

42:26.590 --> 42:27.400
he became

42:27.400 --> 42:28.480
rebellious.

42:29.280 --> 42:31.840
He's going to study abroad?

42:31.840 --> 42:33.030
Yes, he is.

42:33.440 --> 42:34.960
His parents reached an agreement

42:35.000 --> 42:36.630
on his future plans.

42:37.150 --> 42:38.510
He'll go to France to study

42:38.630 --> 42:40.510
and become a good doctor.

42:41.320 --> 42:43.150
He fails

42:43.150 --> 42:44.000
most of his papers

42:44.000 --> 42:45.510
because he doesn't care about them.

42:45.960 --> 42:47.280
But he focuses a lot

42:47.280 --> 42:48.960
on learning a foreign language.

42:49.960 --> 42:51.110
If all goes as planned,

42:52.510 --> 42:53.840
he'd settle abroad.

43:28.180 --> 43:31.870
♪Perhaps♪

43:32.380 --> 43:38.080
♪The more we care,
the more careful we become♪

43:39.220 --> 43:44.620
♪Counting the distance
that separates us♪

43:45.620 --> 43:51.180
♪A single step,
and we'd be closer still♪

43:56.850 --> 44:00.520
♪In the future♪

44:00.980 --> 44:06.700
♪Time will reveal this secret♪

44:08.200 --> 44:13.270
♪Waiting is a silent promise♪

44:14.520 --> 44:19.680
♪That never expires♪

44:23.280 --> 44:27.750
♪Turns out that what's on my mind♪

44:28.750 --> 44:32.420
♪Is your name♪

44:32.920 --> 44:38.020
♪The only stubbornness in my heart♪

44:39.100 --> 44:42.320
♪At first sight♪

44:42.750 --> 44:46.030
♪The future has been determined♪

44:46.720 --> 44:52.280
♪Dreams began to feel real♪

44:53.380 --> 44:56.920
♪Turns out that what's on your mind♪

44:57.380 --> 45:01.320
♪Is a place♪

45:01.620 --> 45:07.180
♪Where the same story is held dear♪

45:07.850 --> 45:11.220
♪Fortunately, I'm not sensible enough♪

45:11.550 --> 45:15.020
♪Courage wasn't late too♪

45:15.550 --> 45:21.620
♪Only then does time not betray
our acquaintance♪
